      <title>[인사] 한국도로교통공단 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/12/12/ZSYCIAWEHJFNRFDWKFFNY4OFSE/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/12/12/ZSYCIAWEHJFNRFDWKFFNY4OFSE/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
